    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Painkiller》是经典同名系列游戏的现代重塑版，拥有最多三人参与的在线合作模式和离线模式。你将在精致的哥特风地图中与海量的恶魔和怪物作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于违背了天意，你被判罚到炼狱中。但是造物主的圣音给予你一个自我救赎的机会。你将扮演一名罪斗士，阻止堕落天使阿撒兹勒向地球派遣恶魔军团的计划。成千上万的敌人想消灭你，其中包括具有独特力量的恶魔，和阿撒兹勒的三个邪魔之子-奈菲林人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会完成使命，获得救赎吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >炼狱乐园——在敌群中纵情跳跃，冲刺和牵引，使用大量全新和经典的《Painkiller》武器来消灭敌人吧。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300120/extras/137a74a406b7f6fe486cc6445ccf9bd8.poster.avif?t=1769070943\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300120/extras/137a74a406b7f6fe486cc6445ccf9bd8.webm?t=1769070943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300120/extras/137a74a406b7f6fe486cc6445ccf9bd8.mp4?t=1769070943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恐惧来袭——从成群的小恶魔到巨怪，你将挑战形形色色的敌人。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300120/extras/5353c3adfead1543369cc88372319fbc.poster.avif?t=1769070943\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300120/extras/5353c3adfead1543369cc88372319fbc.webm?t=1769070943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300120/extras/5353c3adfead1543369cc88372319fbc.mp4?t=1769070943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >释放痛苦——利用塔罗牌来提高你的能力，将其与其他玩家结合以消灭你的敌人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300120/extras/3ea5c162c602ab6ab43c8b68a425eada.poster.avif?t=1769070943\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300120/extras/3ea5c162c602ab6ab43c8b68a425eada.webm?t=1769070943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300120/extras/3ea5c162c602ab6ab43c8b68a425eada.mp4?t=1769070943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谨慎选择你的角色——在四个各具特色的角色：印客、虚无、索尔、罗克之中做出选择，利用各自的特性强化能量、生命值、力量和伤害。<br>叛逆天使模式-脱离主剧情，踏入炼狱的新领域。与好友组队，在手制的随机竞技场中杀出一条生路。</p>",
